name: Olof
description: Functional and water-resistant cross-body bag constructed from 100% recycled polyester. The bag is designed with two inner pockets, a removable and adjustable shoulder strap, and a handle on top. Perfect as an extra bag or for those days when you only need to pack the essentials.

name: Dante Vegan
description: Dante Vegan is a spacious and water- resistant rolltop backpack designed for everyday use, whether you're commuting to work or out in nature. Dante Vegan is a version of our best-selling model Dante, but made without leather details and in 100% recycled and vegan materials. The bag is closed with a metal buckle and can hold between 16â€“23 L.

name: Tony Vegan
description: Backpack in 100% recycled polyester. The bag features a 15inch laptop pocket, one outer zipper pocket, and can carry up to 13 L. Functional and with a minimal yet stylish approach to design, this backpack is a perfect everyday companion.

name: Kurt
description: Kurt is a minimalist, versatile, and durable rolltop backpack, perfect for daily use. Crafted from water-resistant 100% recycled polyester, it's enhanced with fine leather details. The backpack has adjustable shoulder straps and a hidden external zippered compartment.

name: Jack
description: Water-resistant and functional backpack constructed from 100% recycled polyester. It features a 15inch laptop compartment and can carry up to 17 L. The bag is designed with several functional outer and inner pockets. This bag is a modern classic to be worn every day or for those weekend hikes.

name: Walter
description: Water-resistant and spacious backpack constructed in 100% recycled polyester. It features a 16inch laptop compartment and can carry up to 19 L.

name: Antonia
description: Antonia is a sleek and timeless rolltop backpack made of aniline-dyed full-grain leather from Northern Europe. In the main compartment, there is a zippered pocket and four open pockets. The smaller pockets can accommodate a mobile phone, and the largest pocket fits most laptops up to 14 inches.

name: Noa
description: Lightweight rolltop backpack made from 100% recycled nylon ripstop.The bag is constructed with a 13'' laptop pocket and a pocket for camelback, adjustable shoulder straps, and a reflective logo.

name: Iris
description: Iris is a classic and elegant tote bag, made of aniline-dyed full-grain leather from Northern Europe. The bag is unlined and can hold up to 15 liters, as well as accommodating most laptops up to 16 inches. Designed with wide handles and a removable shoulder strap, so you can carry it in multiple ways

name: Louie
description: Technical backpack in crinkled twill made from 100% recycled nylon with either rolltop or canoe closure. The bag features a large mesh pocket and cord details for fastening your yoga mat, making the commute from work to workout a breeze.

name: Jack
description: Water-resistant and functional backpack constructed from 100% recycled polyester. It features a 15inch laptop compartment and can carry up to 17 L. The bag is designed with several functional outer and inner pockets. This bag is a modern classic to be worn every day or for those weekend hikes.

name: Aste
description: This water-resistant and functional bum bag from our Urban Outdoor series is constructed from 100% recycled polyester with leather patch details. The functional and versatile features and heritage leather patch details makes this bag a modern classic to be worn everyday.
